extern player_name
extern player_gold

save visit_count = 0
save reputation = 50

temp greeting = "Welcome"

set visit_count = 1

{greeting}, {player_ame}! This is visit number {visit_count}.
I see you have {player_gold} gold coins.
Your reputation is {reputation}.

temp lucky_number = 7
temp price = 19.99
temp is_vip = false

Your lucky number is {lucky_number}.
Special price today: {price} gold.
VIP status: {is_vip}.

What would you like to do?

- Ask about the village
  You asked about the village.
  - Learn about history
    The village was founded 200 years ago by settlers.
    They built the inn first, then everything else.
  - Ask about shops
    There's a blacksmith near the square.
    The general store is just past the well.
  That's all I know about this place.

- Look for work
  Looking for work, {player_name}?
  - Help with deliveries (5 gold)
    temp reward = 5
    You help carry packages around town.
    Here's {reward} gold for your trouble!
    set reputation = 60
    The townsfolk appreciate your help.
    Reputation now: {reputation}.
  - Guard duty (10 gold)
    temp reward = 10
    Brave of you to volunteer!
    You stand watch through the night.
    Here's {reward} gold for your service.
    set reputation = 70
    The guards speak highly of you.
    Reputation now: {reputation}.
  Thanks for helping out.

- Just passing through
  temp farewell = "Safe travels"
  {farewell}, {player_name}!

Summary: {player_name}, gold={player_gold}, reputation={reputation}.
Come back anytime!
